  <brief_title>Health-related Quality of Life in General Slovenian Population</brief_title>
  <official_title>Health-related Quality of Life in General Slovenian Poplation Assessed by the European Organisation for Research and Treatment of Cancer (EORTC) Core Quality-of-Life Questionnaire QLQ-C30</official_title>
